(29, '전기/전자장비', '측정시험장비', '전자파측정시험장비', '1. 고주파 RF Power Amplifier: 1ea -Output power: 40W min. -Flatness: ±10dB max. -Frequency range: 18 to 40GHz -Input for rated output: 1.0mW max. -Gain: 46dB min. -Gain adjustment: 35dB min. -VSWR: 2.0:1 max. -Mismatch tolerance: Output power foldback protection at reflected power exceeding 10W. Will operated without damage or oscillation with any magnitude and phase of source and load impedance. May oscillate with unshielded open due to coupling to input. Should not be tested with connector off. -Modulation capability: Will faithfully reproduce AM, FM, or pulse modulation appearing on the input signal. AM peak envelope power limited to specified power -Noise power density: -60dBm/Hz max. -Harmonic distortion: -3dBc typ. (at 18GHz) -Primary power: 190-265VAC, single phase, 47/63Hz -Connectors: RF input K(f) on rear panel, RF output – WRD-180 waveguide flange on rear panel Sample ports – K(f) on rear panel -Interface: GPIB, Interlock -Cooling: Forced air(self contained fans), air entry and exit in rear -Weight: ≦30kg -Size(W x H x D): ≦51 x 17 x 69cm 2. External Dual Directional Coupler: 1ea -Frequency range: 18 to 40GHz -Power: 500W CW max., 3kW peak max. -Coupling factor: 50dB ±2dB -Coupling flatness: ±1.0dB -Directivity: 25dB min. -Insertion loss: 0.6dB max. -VSWR: 1.2:1 max. -Connector: WRD-180 C24 3. High Gain Horn Antenna: 1ea -Frequency range: 18 to 40GHz -Max. power input: 450W CW max., 2000W peak max. -Power gain: 15.2 to 22dBi -VSWR: 1.5:1 max. -Connector: WRD 180 C24 waveguide -Mounting provisions: waveguide flange -Waveguide cable(2m, 18~40GHz): 1ea', '고주파 RF 파워증폭기', 'High RF Power Amplifier', 'https://www.zeus.go.kr/storage/images/equip/photo/202210/20221011104126875.jpg', null, '전자파시험동', null, 31),
